name: Liquidate
description:
ART ASSETS DO NO BELONG TO ME

Made for Pre-Made Jam #4 ("Liquid")

The company has gone bankrupt, and you must liquidate your assets. Correctly distribute you assets in a timely manner, otherwise you'll find yourself in some legal trouble!

[How to play]

Click on the assets in the top right to order assets to the floor. Don't call too many though, there are only so many workers available! Click and hold to drag assets to investors. If you give them the incorrect item, or don't give them it in time, they'll leave and you'll lose health.

Music used: "Pixel adventures" by Marcelo Fernandez (https://opengameart.org/content/pixel-adventures)
